      <title>股市崩盘影响回报后，中国量化投资者的资产缩水</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/china-quants-saw-assets-shrink-after-stock-meltdown-hit-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国股市崩盘影响业绩并削弱投资者对其算法驱动交易策略的信心后，中国量化对冲基金上个季度的资产出现自 2022 年底以来的首次下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/china-quants-saw-assets-shrink-after-stock-meltdown-hit-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 07:24:17 GMT</pubDate>
